What you need to know:

Eager motorists from as far as Mombasa, Eldoret, Kisumu and Nakuru made a beeline to enter the farm owned by Lord Delamere familyThe long motorcade caused traffic jam along the highway as the drivers tried to overlap as they made their way to the farmAli Mohammed and his family travelled from Mombasa to Soysambu to come and watch the rally cars in action as they spilled dust in the farm popularly known for beef cows